[ETYC0372193] Error: `@no_inline` is not allowed on a function whose name starts with `_`
    ╭─[ compiler-test:11:4 ]
    │
 11 │ fn _foo() -> u32 {
    │ 
    │ Help: Remove the `@no_inline` annotation or rename the function so it does not start with `_`.
